comments: This is a short song lasting 1:39.  Waylon sings all of the vocals up until the 1:26 mark when Willie finishes out the song.  On Waylon's March 1974 "This Time" album, Willie Nelson was not credited. However, the exact same performance was released on the Dec 1975 "Good Hearted Woman" single and on the Jan 1976 "Wanted! The Outlaws" album as a "Waylon & Willie" performance. SHS credits this as a joint performance to not give the appearance that there were two different versions (i.e., a Waylon solo and a Waylon & Willie duet).
